The paper focuses on identifying influential software changes, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also proposes a machine learning approach to identify these changes, which involves programming languages (cs.PL) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper analyzes commit logs and file centrality, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and social networks (cs.SI).
